OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry and mostly
OL,6,Fcloudy day with misty patches
OL,7,Fpossible, mainly around Shetland, and
OL,8,Flight winds. Sunny spells developing
OL,9,Fover Orkney through the afternoon but
OL,10,Fstaying cloudy for Shetland.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry night with late evening
OL,13,Fsunshine and largely clear skies for
OL,14,FOrkney. Shetland will start cloudy but
OL,15,Flong clear spells developing later in
OL,16,Fthe night. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
