OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA dry day with largely
OL,6,Fclear skies and plenty of sunshine on
OL,7,Foffer. Maybe some patchy high level
OL,8,Fcloud turning sunshine hazy over
OL,9,FShetland. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,12,Fand settled Thursday and Friday with
OL,13,Fvariable cloud and sunny spells. A
OL,14,Fmostly cloudy day on Saturday with
OL,15,Fshowers possible. Breezy on Thursday,
OL,16,Fotherwise light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
